Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A short circuit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the fire extinguisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job was to shoot Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have changed your mind Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ants...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.02,0:01:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all like ants running away from the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.86,0:01:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! This is amazing, Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.49,0:01:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.13,0:01:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a look, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.27,0:01:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The books!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the books will burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.07,0:01:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all running around...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:02:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trampling one another, as if each\Nis more important than the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fear in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he can kill his first person or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is where the path splits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Between whether he can use a gun or not, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you taught how to shoot a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.85,0:03:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were self-taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never fired a gun before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always pull the trigger twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your chance of killing your \N target will rise dramatically!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you can't do that..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't expect to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to... shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only give life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking life is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always pull the trigger twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:44.15,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(279,200)\pos(357,362)}The Monster In My Sight
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... wasn't shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trembling... has stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's too much smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't get away again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't open from this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please calm down and act rationally!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to the security guards and line up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doors are all locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, escort Mr. Schuwald \N out of here, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you secured an evacuation route?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you going to take Mr. Schuwald\Nthrough the sea of fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock down the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sirl
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many books are burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flames are trying to engulf everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you wanted to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied with simply presenting\Nthis image of hell to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the same way you showed me things\Nwhen you read books to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't your aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to become my replacement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided against that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something else came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not scared, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you can barely see \N if I get this close to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what's reflected in my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in a fairy tale country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was walking through that place, \N holding hands with my other half.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like we were the only \N two left in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:09:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have names.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.93,0:10:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot a document.  \N Can you go get it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the mansion and get it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on the desk in my study.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inquiry report concerning the \N death of Margot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helfrich Detective Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margot Langer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real name, Helenka Novakowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.20,0:12:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Born on August 1955 in \N Prague, Czechoslovakia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 1970, at the age of fifteen she illegally immigrated\Nto the former Federal Republic of Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She worked as a so-called \N high-class call girl in Munich:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her clients consisted mainly of\Npoliticians and businessmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and her name became secretly\Nknown among the upper class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her clients included the one who ordered this\Ninvestigation, Mr. Hans Georg Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you're still investigating Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the age of twenty-two, she gave\Nbirth to Mr. Schuwald's child...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen closely to what Mom has to say, okay, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this money and take the train on track five.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay with me, you'll be put in a foster home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay here, people will say\N you're the son of a prostitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said I was abandoned by my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't abandoned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:13:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy went from one foster home to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He suffered a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had wonderful foster parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was always lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they didn't mention \N anything about that in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, Margot Langer remained\Na high-class prostitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but retired in '92.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, before she withdrew from the business...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are indications that she became involved\Nwith the president of the "Bank of Darkness"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this has not been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a side note...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Bank of Darkness laundered money for the \N German underground for five years starting in '91.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.77,0:15:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words it was a nickname\Nfor a black market organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that, held, a monopoly on the process\Nof taking large sums of dirty money...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and exchanging it for safe, legal money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After retiring from being a prostitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margot Langer lived in Offenbach, Hesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a photo of her apartment at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that she lived together with\Nan eighteen year old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the details of their relationship are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On November 2, 1995...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Margot Langer's body was found on Heide Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the police file...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was a random murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the killer was never arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three months before Margot Langer's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she sent a letter to her friend,\Nand I was able to obtain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've attached a copy with this report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is my mom's handwriting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've quit my job and am now living \N a quiet, peaceful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only things I think about in this quiet life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the son I had to part with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my friend who tried to cross the\NCzechoslovakian border with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was caught at the border...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was forcibly dragged back to Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, she gave birth to twins, \N and is now living happily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, I met a young man about the\Nsame age as the son I left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks exactly like my Czechoslovakian friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:17:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with that young man\Nit's like I'm talking to my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's grown into a fine man like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's living happily somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lonely anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad wanted me to read this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason she said she didn't hate Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every door is locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dieter, did you call the fire department yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already did!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away from the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.53,0:19:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One at a time! Slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Form a line and go out one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the women and the elderly go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how we can ever repay you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two bullets left...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't shoot, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.20,0:22:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.88,0:22:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.02,0:22:31.19,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:44.62,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(188,474)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:44.62,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(191,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:47.58,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:23:01.26,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(189,474)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.58,0:23:01.26,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,19)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:26.12,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(189,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:34.54,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(186,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:37.00,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.76,0:23:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
